==English==
{{wikipediapar|Barnacle (disambiguation)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A [[marine]] [[crustacean]] of the [[subclass]] [[Cirripedia]] that [[attach]]es itself to [[submerged]] [[surface]]s such as tidal rocks or the [[bottom]]s of [[ship]]s.
# The [[barnacle goose]].
# {{rfv-sense}} A pirate.
# {{obsolete}} An instrument like a pair of [[pincers]], to fix on the nose of a vicious [[horse]] while shoeing so as to make it more tractable.
# {{cattag|archaic|UK}} A nickname for [[spectacles]].
# {{cattag|slang|obsolete}} A good job, or snack easily obtained.

